  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bb5\u0bcb \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0baf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bcb \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd. \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bc8. \u0b95\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc0\u0b9f \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Attack on journalists cannot be accepted or justified - Jaffna. University. Faculty of Arts Student Union",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna University Faculty of Arts Students' Union said that the attack on journalists in Colombo cannot be accepted or justified.",
        "This has been stated in the media statement issued by the Faculty of Arts Students' Union after the protest in front of Jaffna University.",
        "Media repression has been unleashed in the North East for over 30 years. 39 journalists have been killed in the North East so far.",
        "Media organizations have also been attacked. A significant number of journalists have fled the country out of fear. Till this time the media industry is seen as a critical industry.",
        "It is in this situation that the incident of attack on journalists in Colombo has been reported again. While the attacks are seen as a test for journalists in the Northeast, they are reverberating in Colombo.",
        "In this situation, we cannot accept or justify the attack on journalists in Colombo as we have condemned the disappearances, murders and threats against journalists in the North-East.",
        "In such a way, besides conveying our strong condemnation, the attacked journalists should get due justice. Our Jaffna University College of Arts Students' Union has been active for a long time in all levels of problems faced by the Tamil people.",
        "In that way, the participation of the media during these activities is also seen to be intertwined with our Faculty of Arts Student Union.",
        "As the Jaffna University Faculty of Arts Students' Union, we are insisting that the government administration should confirm it."
      ],
